The following 25Live reference data no longer matches the hardcoded constants in app/lib/twenty_five_live/.
These constants are treated as "rarely change" — please review whether the constants need updating.

<% @drifts.each do |drift| %>
========================================
<%= drift[:entity] %>
========================================
<% if drift[:added].any? %>
ADDED (present in 25Live, missing from constants):
<% drift[:added].each do |item| %>
  - id=<%= item[:id] %> "<%= item[:name] %>"
<% end %>
<% end %>
<% if drift[:removed].any? %>
REMOVED (in constants, no longer in 25Live):
<% drift[:removed].each do |item| %>
  - id=<%= item[:id] %> "<%= item[:name] %>"
<% end %>
<% end %>
<% if drift[:changed].any? %>
CHANGED (same id, different fields):
<% drift[:changed].each do |item| %>
  - id=<%= item[:id] %> "<%= item[:name] %>"
    was:  <%= item[:was].inspect %>
    now:  <%= item[:now].inspect %>
<% end %>
<% end %>
<% end %>

